format: A data frame with 10000 observations on the following 2 variables.
title: Simulated Google search experiment
description:
Description
The data were simulated to look like sample results from a Google search
experiment.
reference:
library(ggplot2)

table(gsearch$type, gsearch$outcome)

ggplot(gsearch, aes(x = type, fill = outcome)) +
  geom_bar(position = "fill") +
  labs(y = "proportion")

parameters.outcome: a factor with levels current test 1 test 2
parameters.type: a factor with levels new search no new search
